Document: Joint3D
Path: godot/classes/class_joint3d.rst
Summary: Abstract base class for all 3D physics joints.

Inherits: Node3D < Node < Object
Inherited By: ConeTwistJoint3D, Generic6DOFJoint3D, HingeJoint3D, PinJoint3D, SliderJoint3D

Abstract base class for all 3D physics joints. Provides common functionality for connecting RigidBody3D nodes with constraints. All specific joint types (ConeTwist, Hinge, Slider, etc.) inherit from this class to implement their unique constraint behaviors. Used in physics simulations to create mechanical connections between objects while maintaining control over movement limitations and reaction forces.
