Summary: Properties and member variables of the Joint3D class with their types, descriptions, and default values.

- exclude_nodes_from_collision (bool): Controls whether nodes are excluded from collision. Default: true
- node_a (NodePath): First node connected to the joint. Default: NodePath("")
- node_b (NodePath): Second node connected to the joint. Default: NodePath("")
- solver_priority (int): Priority for the physics solver. Higher values mean earlier processing. Default: 1
